OL,7,FSuresh Vaghela was just 20-years-old
OL,8,Fand a few weeks into his first term at
OL,9,Funiversity in when he was told he had
OL,10,FHIV during a phone call. It was 1983.
OL,12,FThe doctor told him to go home, tell
OL,13,Fhis family and get his paperwork in
OL,14,Forder as he had only two or three
